    <summary>Improve CLV and reduce churn with Sailthru&#x2019;s high-performance email, mobile marketing, site personalization and predictive intelligence.</summary>
    <description>This extension enables you to fully integrate with Sailthru's powerful suite of products:&#xD;
&#xD;
- Automatically deploy Sailthru Javascript (Horizon or Sailthru Script Tag).&#xD;
- Add all users into the Sailthru system on login or registration.&#xD;
- Hook Magento's newsletter subscriptions into a Sailthru list.&#xD;
- Deliver Magento transactionals through Sailthru for enhanced deliverability, tracking, and user flows.&#xD;
- Create custom Sailthru templates for Customer Signup, Newsletter Signup, Order Confirmation, and Shipping.&#xD;
- Capture customers order data with adjustments and Sailthru campaign attribution.&#xD;
- Deliver abandoned cart emails for known users.&#xD;
</description>
    <notes>This update enables a Beta feature for adding a new Sailthru mass action for the product catalog. Send bulk updates to the Sailthru content library for a given store. &#xD;
&#xD;
* Note: This is beta functionality and may take longer than two minutes to complete, you may also see memory issues on the request. Please report any issues. *</notes>
